Home</h1><ul class="meta"><li> Year: <em>2010</em><a href=""></a></li><li> Client: <em></em><a href="http://www.villandryhome.co.uk">Villandry Home</a></li><li> Tools: <em>Photoshop, Illustrator</em><a href=""></a></li><li><em></em><a href=""></a></li></ul></div><div class="major"><p>Specialising in homeware and gifts, Villandry Home offers a true mix of luxury objects, combining contemporary and classical items from a modest store in West Sussex. Villandry approached Weedoo Media in search of a full eCommerce package, a lightweight CMS and scalable layout.</p><p>The final site is a clean, sophisticated store that takes advantage of high-end photography and pack shots. CSS3 'multiple backgrounds' offers attractive hover transitions to better view each item and a custom Drupal CMS served as an ideal platform for the store team to update stock and edit descriptions.</p></div></section><section class="project"><div class="page-project"><figure class="media  media-layout  media-layout--screen"><img class="image" src="http://localhost:8888/content/2.work/3.villandry/001.081114000900.jpg" alt="001" width="1200" height="868"/></figure><figure class="media  media-layout  media-layout--screen"><img class="image" src="http://localhost:8888/content/2.work/3.villandry/002.081114000900.jpg" alt="002" width="1200" height="1434"/></figure><figure class="media  media-layout  media-layout--screen"><img class="image" src="http://localhost:8888/content/2.work/3.villandry/003.081114000900.jpg" alt="003" width="1200" height="1218"/></figure></div></section><section class="pagination"><a class="pagination-item" href="../../work/portr/"><h2>&#8592 Portr Carry Goods</h2></a><a class="pagination-item" href="../../work/rmn-design-tool/"><h2>Preview Tool &#8594</h2></a></section></body><script src="/public/js/libs/jquery-1.10.2.min.js"></script><script src="/public/js/libs/modernizr.min.js"></script><script src="/public/js/libs/scripts.js"></script></html>